description: Thousands of people protested in support of Robert S. Mueller III’s Russia investigation on Thursday. The protests came a day after the president replaced former Attorney General Jeff Sessions with Matthew G. Whitaker, a Trump loyalist and vocal critic of Mr. Mueller.
title: ‘Hands Off Mueller’: Protests Break Out Nationwide
